<plot>Set in Bra-Arama, Birmingham's scarpiest lingerie outlet, and filmed in Pantavision, Dirty Phonecalls is the new 10-minute comedy from acclaimed director Justin Edgar and cult writer Mike Dent. Dirty Phonecalls was premiered at the 1998 Birmingham Film Festival where it walked away with the prestigious BBC Drama Award. "Dirty Phonecalls makes it cool to be a Brummie" - Birmingham Post "The Height of Brummie kitsch" - Sassy Shorts</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?151434</url></doc>
